title: Firearms Expert Reacts To Counter-Strike 2’s Guns PART 2
description:
Jonathan Ferguson, a weapons expert and Keeper of Firearms & Artillery at the Royal Armouries, breaks down more of the weaponry of Counter-Strike 2, including the R8 Revolver, M4A4, and MAG-7. We even traumatize Jonathan a little with a peculiar PP-Bizon!

0:00 - Intro
0:25 - M4A4
1:37 - Five-SeveN
3:01 - MAG-7
4:44 - CZ75-Auto
7:43 - PP-Bizon
9:12 - MP9
10:54 - Galil AR
12:18 - SG 553
14:15 - SSG 08
16:14 - R8 Revolver
17:27 - P90
18:19 - Tec9
20:11 - Outro

In the latest video in the Firearm Expert Reacts series, Jonathan Ferguson--a weapons expert and Keeper of Firearms & Artillery at the Royal Armouries--breaks down more of the guns of Counter-Strike 2 and  compares them to their real-life counterparts.

Firearms Expert Reacts playlist - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y4T78VQoWUs&list=PLpg6WLs8kxGMgYb13XjPgOKbm5O-CDq7R

If you're interested in seeing more of Jonathan's work, you can check out more from the Royal Armouries right here. - https://www.youtube.com/user/RoyalArmou
